{"tid":2327103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[香港人表示再細啲都仲夠]「472呎單位夠一家四口住」文在寅言論氣炸韓國人","createTime":"2020-12-15T23:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T01:35:03.000Z","uid":204533,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e2fc13527e69bd283399a5950e10f66792a2004b","tid":2327103,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T23:31:37.000Z","msg":"《韓國時報》 （The Korea Times）報導，<strong><span class=\"red\">文在寅近日與國土交通部長金賢美以及土地與住宅公社社長卞彰欽等人視察社會住宅，見到44平方公尺（約13坪  、472.4236呎）房時，文在寅認為這剛好夠兩大人和兩小孩住，隨後引來不少批評，認為這樣的空間，根本不夠容納兩大兩小。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n眼見情況失控，青瓦台急忙澄清，強調文在寅當時只是在詢問卞彰欽，並非指一家四口只能住在44平方公尺大的空間，一切都是保守派媒體斷章取義，民眾還是繼續砲轟，有些人認為文在寅應先從自身做起。青瓦台網站還出現請願，發起人表示，文在寅卸任後和妻子應該住19平方公尺（約5.7坪、204.0011）就夠了。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201214/IJF6A2TICNAP3BCENHGWUZ5LEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201214%2FIJF6A2TICNAP3BCENHGWUZ5LEA%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMUyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=761b811e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201214%2FIJF6A2TICNAP3BCENHGWUZ5LEA%2F&h=fa9eeff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201214/IJF6A2TICNAP3BCENHGWUZ5LEA/</a>"},{"pid":"6cc0f8725780745061472417072d4b2d6d69997e","tid":2327103,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T23:33:05.000Z","msg":"韓國咁大都要起到d樓咁細"},{"pid":"19f5fd572b41f11e535a3bf7db0d9829c49cac2c","tid":2327103,"uid":180462,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cc0f8725780745061472417072d4b2d6d69997e","tid":2327103,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T23:33:05.000Z","msg":"韓國咁大都要起到d樓咁細"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T23:36:34.000Z","msg":"廢撚話 明顯係漢城啦<br />\n香港夠大把廢村啦 幾千銀成棟比你慢慢住 你去囉"},{"pid":"d21a91aca7186cc3e5da82102a7070968e7c4a8a","tid":2327103,"uid":204533,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTi